Introduction

Suzy (수지) is a South Korean singer and dancer. She is a former member of the girl group MAJORS.

Suzy announced that she had left the company on June 2, 2023, after her contract expired.

Her younger brother is FANTASY BOYS's Kim Woo Seok.
